<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
        Deep Search
        <b>converts unstructured PDF documents</b>
        into structured JSON files with accuracy and ease. It enables you to automate knowledge extraction as well as to
        fine-tune your proprietary
        <b>Foundational Models</b>
        and
        <b>Large Language Models</b>. We have already converted and collected the most common open-access repositories of
            technical documents for you to browse and search with ease. In the same way, you can point Deep Search to your
            proprietary document collections to create an
        <b>Enterprise Search</b>
        service.
    </p>
