    <h3 id="collect">Collect</h3>
    <p>
        Deep Search comes pre-loaded with millions of standard technical documents from many public data sources. We adhere to
        all licensing and only provide sources with permissive, open-access licenses. These sources are accessible after
        explicit license confirmation by the user.
    </p>
    <p>
        Document collections are stored and indexed such that you can search and retrieve any document according to their
        contents, down to the values and physical units in tables. These large collections of documents are processed quickly
        and concurrently on scalable cloud infrastructure.
    </p>
